{"tid":263441,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想自殺既巴絲入, 燒炭定跳樓比較好","createTime":"2017-05-30T04:28:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T11:17:38.000Z","uid":44725,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af84a085d7923c14b913fde74ea91ff40cd0c76f","tid":263441,"uid":44725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T04:28:39.000Z","msg":"考慮緊用乜方法<br />\n想安靜咁離去<br />\n<br />\n有無咩提議?"},{"pid":"178d0f2d92a12e993c1066213a46821220791045","tid":263441,"uid":44725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T04:29:03.000Z","msg":"柴灣興華邨和興樓發生燒炭慘劇。下午3時許，一名33歲男子被發現於單位內燒炭，母親大驚報案。他事後由救護車送院搶救，惜告不治。據悉，死者為救護員，未婚，今日休班。警方撿獲一封遺書，正調查其燒炭原因。 <br />\n<br />\n死者的家人其後趕到醫院驚聞噩耗，悲痛不已，其母親更哭呼：「你(死者)掉低我！」有親友透露，只是過時過節大日子才會與事主相聚見面，由於日常見面機會較少，他們也不清楚死者生前有何心事。不過親友不禁慨嘆：「佢(男事主)日常應該有同事可以傾訴，要揀呢條路(燒炭尋死)都無辦法。」"},{"pid":"36ef45debbbda1c242e8e0de3943a226cc545b86","tid":263441,"uid":44725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T04:31:48.000Z","msg":"每日都想死"},{"pid":"37732e39dadcbd7dccd5074cc58866eef2b38b6b","tid":263441,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T04:32:16.000Z","msg":"餓死"},{"pid":"eb4b6f7b3db896f0bab26df2c402681dd270052c","tid":263441,"uid":44725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T04:34:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>餓死</blockquote><br />\n人好似好耐唔食野都唔會死"},{"pid":"125426ddace9e85c0a1e55556c61e37fdef4b411","tid":263441,"uid":42815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T04:36:37.000Z","msg":"人必須要勇敢生存"},{"pid":"e2bee5fd0b3c9470386db2e7c7938f7fe75cf62d","tid":263441,"uid":114271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T04:36:37.000Z","msg":"有冇重視嘅人？"},{"pid":"19f9acc26d35082d3f2aee04aee976cd057770ad","tid":263441,"uid":114271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T04:39:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人<span style=\"color: red;\">總</span>須要勇敢生存</blockquote>"},{"pid":"129ea4a6bdbc8428ebe0d